name: 马赫孙·卡拉贾
name_full: 马赫孙·卡拉贾 Mahsun Karaca
introduction: Mahsun Karaca, also known as "Interview Man", is a Turkish YouTuber and actor. He shoots videos in the genre of agenda, News and Mockumentary.Mahsun Karaca was born on June 25, 1992 in Adana. After completing his education at Adana Çukurova University, Karaca started to produce content by shooting Interview videos, especially for strange and funny news about the agenda. Interview Adam Mahsun Karaca, who was not known enough at first, reached a large audience in early 2018.
